    <item>
      <title>风险成为动荡债务市场的避风港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/risk-becomes-a-safe-haven-in-volatile-debt-market-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在如今混乱的信贷世界中，风险债券在波动时期的表现优于安全债券。原因何在？人们越来越关注利息收入，或者用行业术语来说就是利差。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/risk-becomes-a-safe-haven-in-volatile-debt-market-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
