      <title>马斯克探索利用区块链提高美国政府效率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/musk-exploring-blockchain-use-in-us-government-efficiency-effort</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，埃隆·马斯克已在新成立的政府效率部启动了关于使用区块链技术的讨论。这是特朗普政府为支持数字资产行业而做出努力的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/musk-exploring-blockchain-use-in-us-government-efficiency-effort</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
